{"tid":1140723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高慧然：台灣人的所謂美麗與感動我不懂，我只覺得台灣人很矯情造作","createTime":"2019-05-06T04:41:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T12:00:36.000Z","uid":100680,"like":46,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"68f578fa6aa57b9769ff53bb84d39448da81516d","tid":1140723,"uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T04:41:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20181005/20514785\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181005%2F20514785&d=JxdAuiyzJYRXF2tJvMOkN3Qc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=322fc301\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181005%2F20514785&h=84d52314\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/高慧然/daily/article/20181005/20514785</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20181005/large/e8810a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20181005%2Flarge%2Fe8810a.jpg&h=b5a4e426&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一對年過七十的台灣老人，在攝影師鼓勵下，拍了一輯全裸寫真，主題是愛。攝影師認為愛即是美，而自然的人體就是最美的。於是，這對皮膚鬆弛、肚腩層疊而垂掛、皮膚顏色蒼白微黃毫無生氣的夫婦，在鏡頭前呈現出他們所謂的「美」，拍了一輯相片。那畫面，老實說，令我生理上很不舒服。<br />\n<br />\n就是這麼一輯相片，加上攝影師邏輯奇詭的解說，感動了無數台灣人。可惜，台灣人的感動我完全不懂，整件事，我只覺得極度矯情。<br />\n<br />\n雖然美不美見仁見智，但一定要把垂垂老去的肉體說成真美，卻實在不能令人信服。人類為甚麼一定要自欺欺人呢？當藝術家連承認人體會變老變醜的勇氣都沒有，又怎麼可能拍出真正觸動人心的作品？就直接說身體很醜了，但兩人依然相愛，也比昧着良心說人體很美要好。<br />\n<br />\n至於那對老人，真心相愛，就自己去愛好了，不必剝光衣服證明給旁人看。你們的愛情與他人無關。如果自己的愛情需要不相干的人來肯定，需要剝光衣服來證明，那不是愛情出了問題，就是腦袋出了問題。<br />\n<br />\n美麗並無絕對定義，但人生不同階段，生命會呈現出不同的美麗。<br />\n<br />\n老年人的美，通常是由內向外散發出來的，是來自人生歷練之美，來自於智慧之美，來自於對人生的獨特體悟之美&hellip;&hellip;活到七十歲，沒有內在的美可以啟迪世人，而要剝光衣褲，用所謂的人體的真美來證明自己的價值，那麼，未免叫旁人唏噓。 <br />\n<br />\n高慧然"},{"pid":"24a3c73e1d81edd89d6bc1115c78e69dee1618b5","tid":1140723,"uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:21:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52d6abfd6184725982edb0decae445097aeabd35","tid":1140723,"uid":106119,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:32:45.000Z","msg":"呢D就永遠有高清圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"689f81b7dccb28766b2a3f3fd25d772ef7f9932a","tid":1140723,"uid":53687,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:33:52.000Z","msg":"好似欣宜咁夾硬話肥係靚"},{"pid":"b80ee238d14cddeb83cc907da34bca582b4693bb","tid":1140723,"uid":8636,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:35:44.000Z","msg":"雖然條8婆平時成日講百痴野<br />\n但今次講得岩，事實係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f36d2508f2ab9f7c7178ebcc84abd5f091d9c7","tid":1140723,"uid":7814,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:38:00.000Z","msg":"識閪咩佢！藝術家係咁架啦！<br />\n<br />\n求其掃幾Pat顏料都可以諗到個意景 + 賣一千萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n凌亂嘅筆觸，代表住畫家不安嘅心情<br />\n時重時輕嘅作畫方法，細訴著畫家對社會不公的控訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b00d5ba7e4602c34a5c9bfc87a085236a610ca82","tid":1140723,"uid":170772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T05:38:18.000Z","msg":"老實講 美既定義真係太廣闊<br />\n各人有各自既詮釋 正如人有外在內在美<br />\